<div class="wrapper">
	
	<div class="puzzle-container" id="puzzle-container">

	</div>
	<p class="message" id="message"> </p>
	
	<button id='lockBtn'>Lock Word</button>
	<button id='prevBtn' style="display:none" >Previous</button>
	<button id="solveBtn">Start Solving</button>
	<div></div>
	
	<div id='verbFields'></div>
	<div class="container">
		<h1>
			Guide
		</h1>
		<div class="guide-step">
			<h2>Step 1: Draw the puzzle</h2>
			<p>Draw the puzzle like shown below in image.</p>
			<img src="/images/step1.png"/>
		</div>
		<div class="guide-step">
			<h2>Step 2: Start Solving</h2>
			<p>Click "Start Solving" button. After that, a word will appear in one of the field. If that word fit the context of sentence, click "Lock Word" button. If not, then click next to see other suggestion. You can go to previous word by clicking "Previous" button.</p>
			<img src="/images/step2.png"/>
		</div>
		<div class="guide-step">
			<h2>Step 3: Go to next word</h2>
			<p>After locking the first word, click "Next" button to solve next word. A word will appear in another field. If that word fit the context of sentence, click "Lock Word" button. If not, then click next to see other suggestion. You can go to previous word by clicking "Previous" button.</p>
			<img src="/images/step4.png"/>
		</div>
		<div class="guide-step">
			<h2>Step 4: Repeat</h2>
			<p>Repeat step 2 and 3 until complete puzzle is solved.</p>
		</div>
	</div >
	
	<div class="container">
		<h1>
			Puzzle used in Guide
		</h1>
		<img src="/images/puzzle1.png"/>
		<img src="/images/puzzle2.png"/>
	</div>
</div>



<style>
	.wrapper{
		width: 50%;
		margin:auto;
	}
	.container{
		margin-top: 4rem;
	}
	
	.puzzle-container{
		display: grid;
	}

	.box{
		text-align: center;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}
	
	.input-field{
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
	}
	
	.message{
		height: 5rem;
		margin: 0;
	}
	
	
	.tutorial-video{
		border: 1px solid black;
	}
	div.guide-step p{
		width: 60%;
	}
	div.guide-step img{
		width: 60%;
		border: 1px solid black;
		border-radius: 8px;
		box-shadow: rgb(149 157 165 / 20%) 0px 8px 24px;
	}
</style>
<script src="/js/puzzle_draw.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script src="/js/puzzle_solve.js" type="module"></script>